      • getIsirFieldValueOrNull

        String getIsirFieldValueOrNull(String fieldName)
        Gets the value of an ISIR field.
        Parameters:
        fieldName - The field name. See the list of ISIR field names in the API documentation for possible values.
        Returns:
        The value of the ISIR field, or null if the field does not exist. If field is all spaces, returns a string with all whitespace.

      • getIsirFieldValue

        String getIsirFieldValue(String fieldName)
        Gets the value of an ISIR field.
        Parameters:
        fieldName - The field name. See the list of ISIR field names in the API documentation for possible values.
        Returns:
        The value of the ISIR field, or null if the field name is invalid. If field is all spaces, returns a string with all whitespace.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the field name is invalid.

      • getIsirStatus

        String getIsirStatus()
        Gets the ISIR status. Possible values are:
        • Inactive
        • Pending
        • Unverified
        • Invalid
        • Corrected
        • Valid
        • Undefined
